graph LR
    ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>v1.27.0-rhods-254]

    %% External Dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|distributed state| Etcd[Etcd v3.x<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMesh -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.23+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMesh -.->|metrics config| PromOp[Prometheus Operator v0.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ModelMesh -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager v1.x<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|pull models| Storage[Model Storage<br/>S3/PVC]
    ModelMesh -.->|traffic mgmt| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ModelMesh -->|expose metrics| Monitoring[Monitoring - Prometheus]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| ModelMesh
    KServe[KServe Inference Services] -.->|v1beta1 CR reconciliation| ModelMesh

    %% Runtime Components (integrated)
    ModelMesh -->|serves models via| Triton[Triton Inference Server]
    ModelMesh -->|serves models via| MLServer[MLServer]
    ModelMesh -->|serves models via| OpenVINO[OpenVINO Model Server]
    ModelMesh -->|serves models via| TorchServe[TorchServe]

    %% External Services
    ModelMesh -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    ModelMesh -->|storage access| S3External[S3-compatible Storage<br/>External]

